line_1: The gentle Pilgrims soon aware on't,
line_2: Told 'em their Calling, and their Errant:

line_1: Was bought, you need not doubt on't;
line_2: He could not, I think, get out on't.

line_1: Then clap four slices of Pilaster on't,
